sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant vLLM as vLLM Model Server<br/>metrics port/TCP
    participant Prom as Prometheus / Thanos Querier<br/>9090-9091/TCP HTTPS
    participant WVA as WVA controller-manager<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant EPP as EPP (Endpoint Picker Proxy)<br/>metrics port/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HPA as HPA / KEDA
    participant Admin as Platform Admin
    participant Client as External Client

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over vLLM,HPA: Flow 1: Saturation-Based Autoscaling
        vLLM->>Prom: Expose vllm_kv_cache_usage_fraction,<br/>vllm_scheduler_queue_length,<br/>vllm_avg_output_tokens<br/>(HTTP, in-cluster)
        WVA->>Prom: PromQL queries for vLLM metrics<br/>(HTTPS, TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token SA)
        Prom-->>WVA: Metric values (KV cache, queue depth,<br/>output tokens, request rates)
        Note over WVA: Saturation Engine runs analysis:<br/>V1 (% KV cache) or V2 (absolute tokens)<br/>or Queueing Model (M/M/c theory)<br/>→ Pipeline: Optimizer → Limiter → Enforcer<br/>→ Emits wva_desired_replicas metric
        WVA->>Prom: Prometheus scrapes /metrics<br/>(HTTPS/8443, TLS, Bearer Token)
        HPA->>Prom: Read wva_desired_replicas external metric<br/>(HTTPS, TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token)
        Prom-->>HPA: Desired replica count
        HPA->>K8sAPI: Update scale subresource<br/>(HTTPS/6443, TLS 1.2+, SA token)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Client,K8sAPI: Flow 2: Scale-from-Zero
        Client->>EPP: Request to scaled-down model<br/>(HTTP/gRPC)
        Note over EPP: Queue builds up while<br/>replicas == 0
        WVA->>EPP: Scrape inference_extension_flow_control_queue_size<br/>(HTTPS, TLS, Bearer Token epp-metrics-reader)
        EPP-->>WVA: Queue size > 0 detected
        Note over WVA: Scale-from-zero engine:<br/>Check DecisionCache for cooldown<br/>→ Scale target replicas directly
        WVA->>K8sAPI: Update Deployment scale subresource<br/>(HTTPS/6443, TLS 1.2+, SA token)
        WVA->>K8sAPI: Update VA status with scale event<br/>(HTTPS/6443, TLS 1.2+, SA token)
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over Admin,WVA: Flow 3: Dynamic Configuration Update
        Admin->>K8sAPI: Update ConfigMap<br/>(e.g. wva-saturation-scaling-config)<br/>(HTTPS/6443, TLS 1.2+, user creds)
        K8sAPI-->>WVA: ConfigMap watch event
        Note over WVA: ConfigMap Reconciler:<br/>3-tier resolution:<br/>namespace-local > global > defaults<br/>→ Update in-memory Config
        Note over WVA: Next saturation cycle<br/>uses updated config<br/>(no restart needed)
    end
